text: Wiesenttal is a municipality in the district of Forchheim in Bavaria in Germany. == Municipal subdivisions == Wiesenttal is divided into 21 parishes: * Albertshof * Birkenreuth * Draisendorf * Engelhardsberg * Gößmannsberg * Haag * Kuchenmühle * Muggendorf * Neudorf * Niederfellendorf * Oberfellendorf * Rauhenberg * Schottersmühle * Störnhof * Streitberg * Trainmeusel * Voigendorf * Wartleiten * Wohlmannsgesees * Wöhr * Wüstenstein ==References== Category:Forchheim (district)
title: Wiesenttal
